Title: One Traveler's Misfortune
Description:
Did you have to throw our supplies at them?! Why not use your weapon? Maybe fancy spells or kicks? Why the supplies?!

Now we don't have enough to last us, especially with Nephew Bentnail here. His appetite is like a yeti's!

You threw it, you get us more. There is wreckage down the path. Maybe you will find supplies there.
ObjectivesText: Search the Abandoned Wreckage for supplies.
CompletionText: Nephew Bentnail has already eaten two days worth of food. I hope you found us more!
RewardText:
You were attacked by a mogu? That sounds terrible!

I hate to ask, but did you manage to pick up any supplies while you were fighting for your life?

No?! This is very bad luck.

Objectives.Text: Search the Abandoned Wreckage for supplies
